snippet.title: Seth MacFarlane Has No Time for Astrology & Tattoos
snippet.description:
Kristen Wiig, Seth MacFarlane and James dive into the validity of astrology before James asks Kristen how she began with a small tattoo she was unsure about and ended with a much larger one she's ultimately getting removed.

Each week night, THE LATE LATE SHOW with JAMES CORDEN throws the ultimate late night after party with a mix of celebrity guests, edgy musical acts, games and sketches.
